@startuml C1_Process_View_US_2_2_6
!include <C4/C4_Container>

title C1 — Contexto | Vista de Processos — US 2.2.6 Manage Representatives

Person(portOfficer, "Port Authority Officer", "Creates, updates and deactivates representatives")
System(api, "Port Management API", "Part of PLMS")

' === Create Representative ===
portOfficer -> api : 1. POST /api/shipping-agents/{taxNumber}/representatives\n(CreateRepresentativeDTO)
api --> portOfficer : 2. 201 Created (RepresentativeDTO)

' === Update Representative ===
portOfficer -> api : 3. PUT /api/shipping-agents/{taxNumber}/representatives/{id}\n(UpdateRepresentativeDTO)
api --> portOfficer : 4. 200 OK (Updated RepresentativeDTO)

' === Deactivate Representative ===
portOfficer -> api : 5. POST /api/shipping-agents/{taxNumber}/representatives/{id}/deactivate
api --> portOfficer : 6. 204 No Content (Representative deactivated)

@enduml
